https://scholar.google.com/        --> Most common one. 

https://www.mendeley.com/search/   --> An alternative for searching.

https://hal.archives-ouvertes.fr/  --> An alternative for searching.

https://www.connectedpapers.com/   --> A great tool for searching for similar papers with a graph.

https://www.litmaps.co/            --> Another website for visual research navigation, citation network search, and team synchronization.

https://labml.ai/                  --> You can search the newest AI-related papers using recent, daily, weekly and monthly ways. 
                                       Additionally, helps for monitoring deep learning model training and hardware usage from your mobile phone.

https://www.readcube.com/home      --> A good tool for discovering, organising, reading, annotating, sharing and citing.
